@startuml
[*] --> InitialState
InitialState --> Registered : registration completed
Registered --> LoggedIn : valid login
LoggedIn --> DocumentUpload : upload document
DocumentUpload --> DocumentUpload : continue upload [*]
DocumentUpload --> ProfileView : view profile
ProfileUpload --> CertificateApplication : apply for certificate
CertificateApplication --> LoggedIn : reapply for certificate
LoggedIn --> CertificateRequest : request verification
CertificateRequest --> CertificateRequest : continue requesting [*]
LoggedIn --> Ended : log out or finish actions
@enduml
